thread.title: Mr BRENDAN MURRAY.
thread.title_full: Mister-Auto.ie reviewed by Mr BRENDAN MURRAY.

author: Mr BRENDAN MURRAY.
title: Mr BRENDAN MURRAY.
text: My second time ordering from this supplier. They were totally reliable in their information and prices and the delivery of the product i ordered was prompt. Another supplier from Dundalk had the same product at the same price but when i went to order it they doubled the price. Not so Mister -Auto, they were honest throughout with me and they are very professional.
